{"tid":568718,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（無本生利）委內瑞拉發行加密虛擬貨幣petro","createTime":"2018-02-22T05:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T14:28:31.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3f5e13a0306110d6e5fc747f4a1238a24664c7b0","tid":568718,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T05:04:33.000Z","msg":"陷入經濟危機及嚴重通脹的委內瑞拉發行3,840萬枚加密貨幣「Petro」，是全球首個由政府推出的虛擬貨幣，開售20小時即吸金7.35億美元（57.3億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將為財政拮据的委內瑞拉政府帶來數以十億美元收入，有助抵銷美國制裁影響，以及避免政府再次發債。"},{"pid":"ac248ebebf1f2bf15886b27b1cd3155d7c9e247a","tid":568718,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1207f7c9daeda4feed6773996b8b35a133ff94e2","tid":568718,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7fb83685da41e3f0e0e46aabd32dbd25bec013","tid":568718,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"地獄"},{"pid":"508b9a60e20b143ea416329893a19dda352a11b1","tid":568718,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:10:10.000Z","msg":"拎定午餐肉過去準備屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39eccdfb73b3cffa3dde1da482158f6b6e65cb1a","tid":568718,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1a27b988257506de38aeaa23ee4613d8d210c8","tid":568718,"uid":28845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"508b9a60e20b143ea416329893a19dda352a11b1","tid":568718,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:10:10.000Z","msg":"拎定午餐肉過去準備屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:19:33.000Z","msg":"果度啲女好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f19a202b199d5ba274293361a511f17b1de8d47","tid":568718,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"識玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無本生利,好快一車車國家做爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd7c288142b3edcac828f1a758bf990ba190ed6","tid":568718,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎石油做抵押<br />\n美國買哂都唔奇"},{"pid":"a13b7c55e1a77490def942d832cc364749d2d19d","tid":568718,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"1 枚 Petro 可兌 1 桶原油，單價以今年 1 月中，委內瑞拉原油價格為基礎，定為 60 美元，預計總發行量將達 1 億個。當地總統馬杜羅（Nicolas Maduro）表示，「我們發行了首個有天然資源作擔保的虛擬貨幣」，有消息指在預購首日已獲得 7.35 億美元（約HK$57.33億）認購訂單，但並無進一步透露其他數據及資料。<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉的監管機構亦於上周指， Petro 將會吸引來自卡塔爾、土耳其及其他中東國家，以至歐美等地的的投資者。而 <span style=\"color: red;\">Petro 亦不能以委內瑞拉的當地貨幣購買</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，針對外國投資者。《日本經濟新聞》消息指出，為吸引海外投資者，委內瑞拉政府提供最多 60% 折扣優惠。"}]}